From: Nicolas Fella <nicolas.fella@gmx.de>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:00:56 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Properly link against tesseract

Dynamically loading it at runtime only complicates things, for no apparent benefit
---
